                Hello! My name is Nicholo John L. Batoy, and I am currently a student at Lyceum of Alabang. I am pursuing a Bachelor of Science in Information Technology (BSIT), a choice driven by my fascination with technology and how it shapes our daily lives. Throughout my educational journey, I have been dedicated to building a solid foundation in tech concepts, and this course is providing me with the practical skills and knowledge needed to thrive in the digital age.
